019/04/stephen-king-owen-king-sleeping-beauties-amc-series-1202596914/|title=AMC Makes Pilot Script Deal For Owen & Stephen King Novel \u2018Sleeping Beauties;\u2019 Owen King To Write It|last=Jr|first=Mike Fleming|last2=Jr|first2=Mike Fleming|date=2019-04-16|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2020-01-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/amc-developing-projects-katie-couric-ilana-glazer-stephen-king-scott-z-burns-1202833185/|title=AMC Networks & Studios Developing Projects With Katie Couric, \u2018The Report\u2019s Scott Z. Burns, \u2018Broad City\u2019s Ilana Glazer & Stephen King \u2013 TCA|last=White|first=Peter|last2=White|first2=Peter|date=2020-01-16|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2020-01-20}}</ref>\n|[[Sleeping Beauties (novel)|Based on the novel of the same name]].\n|Sugar23\n|[[AMC (TV channel)|AMC]]\n|-\n| ''[[The Stand (upcoming miniseries)|The Stand]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://comicbook.com/horror/2019/09/13/the-stand-adaptation-director-shares-teaser-announce-start-production|title=The Stand Adaptation Director Shares Teaser to Announce Start of Production|website=www.comicbook.com|language=en-US|access-date=2019-09-15}}</ref>\n| [[The Stand|Based on the novel of the same name]]. \n| CBS Television Distribution\n| [[CBS]]\n|-\n|[[Overlook (TV series)|''Overlook'']]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://collider.com/the-shining-tv-series-overlook-jj-abrams-hbo-max/|title='The Shining' Spinoff Series 'Overlook' in the Works at J.J. Abrams' Bad Robot, HBO Max|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|date=2020-04-16|website=Collider|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-17}}</ref>\n|Spin-off series based on [[The Shining (novel)|''The Shining'']]\n|Warner Bros. Television\n|[[HBO Max]]\n|}\n\n==Derivative works==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" width=\"100%\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Films\n! Director\n! Notes\n! Distributor\n! [[Rotten Tomatoes|RT]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1980s\n|-\n| 1987\n| ''[[A Return to Sal