atoes.com/m/mist/|title=The Mist (2007)|website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2019-01-05}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[No Smoking (2007 film)|No Smoking]]''\n| [[Anurag Kashyap]]\n| Based on the short story \"[[Quitters, Inc.]]\"\n| [[Eros International]]\n| 46%<ref>{{cite web |title=No Smoking (2007) |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1192358-1192358-no_smoking |website=Rotten Tomatoes}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''[[Dolan's Cadillac (film)|Dolan's Cadillac]]''\n| Jeff Beesley\n| [[Dolan's Cadillac (short story)|Based on the novella of the same name]].\n| G2 Pictures\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{sort|2010|2010s}}\n|- \n| 2013\n| ''[[Carrie (2013 film)|Carrie]]''\n| [[Kimberly Peirce]]\n| Based on the novel of the same name. \n| [[Sony Pictures Motion Picture Group|Sony Pictures Releasing]]\n| 50%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/carrie/|title=Carrie (2013)|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango Media]]|accessdate=April 5, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2014\n| {{sort|Good Marriage|''[[A Good Marriage (film)|A Good Marriage]]''}}\n| [[Peter Askin]]\n| [[A Good Marriage|Based on the novella of the same name]]. \n| [[Screen Media Films]]\n| 32%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stephen_kings_a_good_marriage/|title=A Good Marriage (2014)|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=November 4, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Mercy (2014 film)|Mercy]]''\n| [[Peter Cornwell (director)|Peter Cornwell]]\n| Based on the short story \"[[Gramma (short story)|Gramma]]\". \n| [[Universal Studios]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Cell (film)|Cell]]''\n| [[Tod Williams (filmmaker)|Tod Williams]]\n| [[Cell (novel)|Based on the novel of the same name]]. \n| [[Saban Capital Group|Saban Films]]\n| 11%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cell_2016/|title=Cell (2016)|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango Media]]|accessdate=November 5, 2019}}</ref> \n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2017\n| {{sort|Dark Tower|''[[The Dark To