{"title_page": "Pauline Croft", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2016}}\n\n'''Pauline Croft''' is an English historian, professor, and writer. She is a [[reader (academic rank)|reader]] in history at the [[Royal Holloway, University of London]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Pauline Croft|url=http://www.palgrave.com/authors/author-detail/Pauline-Croft/10590/|website=Palgrave Macmillan|accessdate=8 December 2015}}</ref> She has published on the 16th and 17th centuries (part of [[early modern Britain]]) in [[British history]].\n\n==Major works==\n* ''King James'', by Pauline Croft (2003). Published by [[Palgrave Macmillan]]. {{ISBN|978-0-333-61396-2}}\n[[James I of England|James I]] was the first [[House of Stuart|Stuart]] king of England. Croft's book is currently considered the best overview of his reign.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Cramsie|first1=John|title=Reviews in History|url=http://www.history.ac.uk/reviews/review/334|website=History.ac.uk|accessdate=8 December 2015}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Croft, Pauline}}\n[[Category:English historians]]\n\n\n{{England-writer-stub}}\n{{England-historian-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2016}}\n\n'''Pauline Croft''' is an English historian, professor, and writer. She is a [[reader (academic rank)|reader]] in history at the [[Royal Holloway, University of London]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Pauline Croft|url=http://www.palgrave.com/authors/author-detail/Pauline-Croft/10590/|website=Palgrave Macmillan|accessdate=8 December 2015}}</ref> She has published on the 16th and 17th centuries (part of [[early modern Britain]]) in [[British history]].\n\n==Major Works==\n* ''King James'', by Pauline Croft (2003). Published by [[Palgrave Macmillan]]. {{ISBN|978-0-333-61396-2}}\n[[James I of England|James I]] was the first [[House of Stuart|Stuart]] king of England. Croft's book is currently considered the best overview of his reign.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Cramsie|first1=John|title=Reviews in History|url=http://www.history.ac.uk/reviews/review/334|website=History.ac.uk|accessdate=8 December 2015}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Croft, Pauline}}\n[[Category:English historians]]\n\n\n{{England-writer-stub}}\n{{England-historian-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Chris the speller", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eMajor works:replaced: Works \u2192 works", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pauline_Croft"}
